190
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:35,600
Prime Minister, you are so mighty.

191
00:17:35,600 --> 00:17:38,920
If you want to snatch Deep Water Nation’s royal blood in the future,

192
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:42,830
I will definitely help you to win the battle.

193
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:47,370
Lin Yi told me before he died that

194
00:17:47,370 --> 00:17:50,730
Zhan Nancheng is the one behind the loss of the Earth Absorbing Bell,

195
00:17:50,730 --> 00:17:54,560
but Qi Zhen’s men conducted it.

196
00:17:56,330 --> 00:17:58,530
The king is working with Qi Zhen.

197
00:18:00,190 --> 00:18:03,860
I’m not sure how many conspiracies there are behind the loss of Earth Absorbing Bell,

198
00:18:03,860 --> 00:18:05,770
but I understand

199
00:18:05,770 --> 00:18:09,900
