200
00:18:11,410 --> 00:18:14,310
So, I can’t leave Deep Water Nation now.

201
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:18,750
Only if I find Earth Absorbing Bell, Zhan Nancheng will not have any excuse to kill me.

202
00:18:18,750 --> 00:18:21,740
Then, I will have more time to set a trap.

203
00:18:41,340 --> 00:18:44,840
The badge is here and General is here, Ji Yu doesn’t dare to take it.

204
00:18:44,840 --> 00:18:47,370
I order you to enter Heaven Fiend Nation secretly.

205
00:18:47,370 --> 00:18:49,940
Contacting the old troops is a dangerous move.

206
00:18:49,940 --> 00:18:51,940
Once it's known by Zhan Nancheng,

207
00:18:51,940 --> 00:18:54,730
